title: More Dominion systems seized
author: VD
content_html:
From Major Patriot:

BREAKING:  Subpoenas are being issued in Maricopa Country to seize ALL of the Dominion systems for a full forensic audit.

This is significant, because if Dominion voting machines are shown to be shifting votes in a third straight county in three different states, that will prove that the reported election results were, in fact, substantively fraudulent.
